data.description: One owner, well kept, 3 bedroom 2 and a half bath house with a 2 car garage in the beautiful amenity filled Luckey Ranch Subdivision less than 3 miles from 1604 and 8 miles to Lackland AFB. Qualifies for a ZERO down payment USDA loan. VA and FHA buyers welcome. Downstairs kitchen/living areas and master bathroom newly floored with Laminate Vinyl Plank. Very nice 2022 KitchenAid fridge can convey. Oven/Stove was also replaced with a Frigidaire glass top electric with convection and air fry oven. House faces east so the driveway is shaded in the evening and there is a covered patio in the back so you can enjoy the shade or cover from the rain. On quiet street across from a small neighborhood playground. Luckey Ranch has a huge neighborhood park across from its own Elementary school. Park includes playground and swings, full Basketball Court, Baseball Field, 2 Soccer fields with goal posts, multiple gazebos with picnic tables, splashpad, and tranquil pond with catch and release fishing pier, and a walking trail. Security Cameras do not convey.
